{"tid":429764,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】三個強國女人去完韓國整容後出唔到境","createTime":"2017-10-09T08:22:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-09T23:47:33.000Z","uid":75969,"like":394,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":77,"replies":[{"pid":"a660d1ce3c1dcbeb459861bd4523454378c8daa7","tid":429764,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T08:22:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20171009/large/1507511558_2c25.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171009%2Flarge%2F1507511558_2c25.jpg&h=603da6fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n許多中國人趁着黃金周長假出國旅遊，也有人到南韓順便整容，但記得算好「復原」的日子啊！內地女主播建華華昨天在《微博》發文，表示有幾名女子到南韓整容，結果卻在當地機場無法出境，必須等待確認身分。<br />\n<br />\n建華華表示，這是民航人士傳給她的照片。照片中3名女子頭上綁着紗布，臉部樣貌看起來有點怪異，拿着護照在等待，可能是因為整容手術結束不久還沒「康復」，因此必須再確認身分。建華華調侃，「連媽媽都不知道妳是誰」<br />\n。<br />\n網友們也紛紛留言「韓國就這點不好，既然知道自己整容出口，幹嘛不搞個瞳孔識別」、「哇！腫得好厲害」、「像被打腫」、「原諒我不厚道地笑了」、「剛整完容能坐飛機嗎」、「那天從金浦機場回來邊上就坐了兩個，太嚇人了」、「這確定不是毀容嗎」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20171009/57308133\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20171009%2F57308133&d=YWLSRs%2BcVshAsQ1%2FQDMmPTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=5020e75d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20171009%2F57308133&h=9e22b093\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20171009/57308133</a>"},{"pid":"aca351c53cf68e048ad55dae146418f530c74296","tid":429764,"uid":75969,"like":378,"dislike":3,"score":375,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T08:23:04.000Z","msg":"最右邊個個塊臉好似比人用平底鑊一野兜落去兜到扁晒咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b9774e1d67c58570b38e67c64d64f776de8e0bf","tid":429764,"uid":36178,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T08:23:22.000Z","msg":"恐怖分子<img src=\"/